{"tid":1471612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯防暴警察毆打女示威者引公憤 內政部展開內部調查","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:09:12.000Z","uid":133680,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"74bce59949612e2ac1fe6c3254e34a09af7a1056","tid":1471612,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/363365/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F363365%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=97439a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/363365/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯防暴警拳打女示威者 內政部展開內部調查<br />\n<br />\n即時國際<br />\n撰文：梁凱怡<br />\n2019-08-13 20:31<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-08-14 13:59<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯連續多個周末爆發大型示威，抗議政府無理取消反對派候選人參加市議會選舉的資格。社交媒體流傳的片段顯示，一名女示威者被防暴警察帶走時，其中一名警員用拳頭打女示威者，引起爭議。俄羅斯內政部8月12日指，已對個案展開內部調查。<br />\n<br />\n從影片可見，一名年輕女子遭兩名身穿防暴裝備的警察拖行，其中一名警察用拳頭向女示威者的腹部打了一下，之後撿回掉在地上的警棍。<br />\n<br />\nМент бьет кулаком в живот девушке. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/vhHZUix8UV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FvhHZUix8UV&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=33d766ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/vhHZUix8UV</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Ян Кателевский (@ya_YANson) 2019年8月10日<br />\n<br />\n影片中的女示威者、26歲的索斯諾夫卡雅（Daria Sosnovskaya）接受俄羅斯媒體Mediazona網站訪問時指，自己因為抗議警方拘留一名傷殘人士，而被警察拖走。<br />\n<br />\n索斯諾夫卡雅表示，當時警員朝她跑過來。她形容被帶走的過程說：「我極為不舒服，全身開始抽搐，不能呼吸。」她表示，自己之後被帶到警署，與其他被拘留的人關在一起。在警署待了數小時，無法取得律師協助，最後在警告下獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯內政部表示，已針對個案展開內部調查，並承諾「那些有罪之人必須負起責任。」<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯阻撓反對派人士參加莫斯科市議會選舉，引起大規模示威潮，是總統普京（Vladimir Putin）自2012年再次出任總統至今，最大型的抗議活動。過去一個月來，包括獲批和不獲批的大大小小集會撼動莫斯科，10日舉行的最大一次集會，吸引6萬人參加，其中136人被捕。"},{"pid":"5d6dd7b0144e8fe85296234d385a8c3e1347e0b7","tid":1471612,"uid":171992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"067331a17ee0ebd8737b4ef6bcb713eb3c9f30c2","tid":1471612,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef3ce5521b13ed0e629139adf9804f9ae8c1407","tid":1471612,"uid":173326,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"港府係古今中外最殘暴嘅政權，64坦克都叫做曾經嘗試兜過個人，而香港黑警係故意瞄頭射市民仲要鼓勵其他黑警效法"},{"pid":"c64ada772151dd78008b58c9462fe5628c967406","tid":1471612,"uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd688f9294a1bf652a64b76eda96fc98a7c4e568","tid":1471612,"uid":35094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"差撚過俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218978a782364407fa0a684ab6cd6795ef5a0d22","tid":1471612,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"香港人你地醜唔撚醜"},{"pid":"cbecabb43f84ce8a23246f447cbdcef26ad22a89","tid":1471612,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7ef22b7f001d08478a0f17a9dc41164eefb5fa","tid":1471612,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c278942733119908787d0ff0d9f315c217667fd","tid":1471612,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd688f9294a1bf652a64b76eda96fc98a7c4e568","tid":1471612,"uid":35094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"差撚過俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"This is China<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64de53a7df4115e331a2ea2f1d962dff1c3901f7","tid":1471612,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"香港真係仲好意思講法治"},{"pid":"72b652d724812c7ed8d136fb7dacb19e18b03ced","tid":1471612,"uid":116967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"香港而家仲衰過俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點可以唔光復"},{"pid":"0ec448e0856c8168b37ec345d2bc21c6daa73d8f","tid":1471612,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c91f3d357880f5f4aa5fe86e4e5b92bb236119","tid":1471612,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"衰過俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004289c131ea71738195fba1f6c002207b889bb9","tid":1471612,"uid":298622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74bce59949612e2ac1fe6c3254e34a09af7a1056","tid":1471612,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/363365/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F363365%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=97439a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/363365/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯防暴警拳打女示威者 內政部展開內部調查<br />\n<br />\n即時國際<br />\n撰文：梁凱怡<br />\n2019-08-13 20:31<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-08-14 13:59<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯連續多個周末爆發大型示威，抗議政府無理取消反對派候選人參加市議會選舉的資格。社交媒體流傳的片段顯示，一名女示威者被防暴警察帶走時，其中一名警員用拳頭打女示威者，引起爭議。俄羅斯內政部8月12日指，已對個案展開內部調查。<br />\n<br />\n從影片可見，一名年輕女子遭兩名身穿防暴裝備的警察拖行，其中一名警察用拳頭向女示威者的腹部打了一下，之後撿回掉在地上的警棍。<br />\n<br />\nМент бьет кулаком в живот девушке. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/vhHZUix8UV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FvhHZUix8UV&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=33d766ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/vhHZUix8UV</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Ян Кателевский (@ya_YANson) 2019年8月10日<br />\n<br />\n影片中的女示威者、26歲的索斯諾夫卡雅（Daria Sosnovskaya）接受俄羅斯媒體Mediazona網站訪問時指，自己因為抗議警方拘留一名傷殘人士，而被警察拖走。<br />\n<br />\n索斯諾夫卡雅表示，當時警員朝她跑過來。她形容被帶走的過程說：「我極為不舒服，全身開始抽搐，不能呼吸。」她表示，自己之後被帶到警署，與其他被拘留的人關在一起。在警署待了數小時，無法取得律師協助，最後在警告下獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯內政部表示，已針對個案展開內部調查，並承諾「那些有罪之人必須負起責任。」<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯阻撓反對派人士參加莫斯科市議會選舉，引起大規模示威潮，是總統普京（Vladimir Putin）自2012年再次出任總統至今，最大型的抗議活動。過去一個月來，包括獲批和不獲批的大大小小集會撼動莫斯科，10日舉行的最大一次集會，吸引6萬人參加，其中136人被捕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:32:21.000Z","msg":"你睇下香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c446770956888f9b412031ef7630b51a5ccacd6","tid":1471612,"uid":158889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯都查 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da72bd6e0db5148c518f82c7192b134c1a596316","tid":1471612,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c5f024539c4f5f2c692eb46f439dfff12aee10","tid":1471612,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母共產黨"},{"pid":"6799517ea162661e572341ab2dd6c29dca8d90a6","tid":1471612,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c446770956888f9b412031ef7630b51a5ccacd6","tid":1471612,"uid":158889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯都查 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"做下樣都要啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed76167a24018b9ac9f73768f69795ff4c43c9c","tid":1471612,"uid":209097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯都會做下樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ab6b40b6e2ac829b3d938142c01b8e512376fb","tid":1471612,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6799517ea162661e572341ab2dd6c29dca8d90a6","tid":1471612,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c446770956888f9b412031ef7630b51a5ccacd6","tid":1471612,"uid":158889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯都查 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"做下樣都要啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" clas